data.description: Welcome to quiet country living with only 12 miles to downtown Crestview or take the mid bay straight to the beaches!  This home has been well cared for....At just under 2 acres. This home comes with a 30' x 40' electric workshop. Open concept  floor plan and to include a metal roof, spray foam insulation, tankless gas HWH  (new propane Tank (above ground) just filled. Wifi enabled thermo. Also, all tile flooring and custom wood trim throughout. Septic last inspected 2021.  Neighborhood access to 3 spring fed ponds and hiking trails!  Also, new dishwasher, faucet and soft close drawers & cabinets. The kitchen island with the wine cooler STAYS as well as the W/D and both work great.
